      "name": "codebase-map-saas",
      "source": "./plugins/codebase-map-saas",
      "description": "SaaS Onboarding Pack — onboard new engineers to SaaS B2B codebases (CRM, CDP, eCommerce, multi-tenant). Bilingual EN/VI. Skill + 3 slash commands (/saas-onboard, /saas-apis, /saas-tier-logic). Reuses codebase-map MCP tools.",
